-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/session-routing/design.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/session-routing/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/code-execution/design.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/code-execution/spec.md\n\n(Results are truncated: showing first 100 results. Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"count":100,"truncated":true},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z","time":{"start":1775875751963,"end":1775875751978}}}}
