\n| ST-4.31: Documentation | 6 | 3h |\n| **Total** | **257** | **128.5h** |\n\n---\n\n## File Deliverables Checklist\n\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/file_types.go` — File-related type definitions\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/file_errors.go` — File operation error definitions\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/file_config.go` — File manager configuration\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/file_validation.go` — Path validation and security\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/file_manager.go` — FileManager implementation\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/file_batch.go` — Batch operations implementation\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/file_watcher.go` — Directory watching implementation\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/sandbox_file_client.go` — Sandbox file client interface\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/file_manager_test.go` — Unit tests\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/file_manager_integration_test.go` — Integration tests\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/mock_sandbox_file.go` — Mock sandbox file client\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Build verification\ngo build ./pkg/picod/...\n\n# Unit test verification (all picod tests)\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -v\n\n# Specific test suites\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestReadFile -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestWriteFile -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestDeleteFile -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestListDirectory -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestStat -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestMove -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestCopy -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestBatch -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestWatch -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestValidate -v\n\n# Race detection\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -race\n\n# Coverage report\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -cover\n\n# Integration tests (requires Docker/sandbox)\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -tags=integration -v\n```\n\n---\n\n## Definition of Done\n\n- [ ] All 257 tasks complete\n- [ ] `FileManager` interface fully implemented\n- [ ] All path validation rules implemented with tests\n- [ ] All file size and type limits enforced\n- [ ] Directory operations work (list, create, remove, recursive)\n- [ ] File streaming works (ReadFileStream, WriteFileStream)\n- [ ] Batch operations work (stat, delete, copy)\n- [ ] File watching works with event notifications\n- [ ] All error types defined and returned appropriately\n- [ ] Context cancellation respected in all operations\n- [ ] Configuration loaded from environment variables\n- [ ] Unit tests pass (>85% coverage for core files)\n- [ ] Integration tests pass with real sandbox and store\n- [ ] Race detector clean\n- [ ] `go build ./pkg/picod/...` succeeds\n- [ ] Documentation complete with GoDoc\n- [ ] Mock implementations provided for unit testing\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|\n| AR-009: Sandbox Interface | File operations in sandboxes |\n| AR-012: Store Interface | Session resolution |\n| AR-013: Redis Implementation | Store backend option |\n| AR-014: Valkey Implementation | Store backend option |\n| AR-015: PicoD Command Execution | Shared pkg/picod infrastructure |\n| `pkg/common/types` | Shared types |\n\n---\n\n## Design Notes\n\n- **Security first:** All paths validated before any sandbox interaction\n- **Path traversal:** Rejects `../` patterns and normalizes paths\n- **Symlink handling:** Resolves within sandbox context, rejects external targets\n- **Size limits:** Configurable via environment, enforced on both read and write\n- **File types:** Blocked/allowed extensions via configuration\n- **Streaming:** io.ReadCloser/io.Reader interfaces for memory efficiency\n- **Batch operations:** Efficient bulk operations with partial failure handling\n- **File watching:** Event-driven notifications for directory changes\n- **Context aware:** All operations respect context cancellation\n- **Sandbox integration:** Via AR-009 interface\n- **Store integration:** Via AR-012 interface for session resolution\n- **Environment config:** PICOD_* variables for all settings\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_b